snippet.title: Webinar - Surrogacy in Massachusetts
snippet.description:
Are you curious about surrogacy in Massachusetts? If so, this webinar is for you. New England Surrogacy Co-Director Catherine Tucker hosts a discussion all about the topic of surrogacy in the bay state (aka Massachusetts).

Panelists include:

Catherine Tucker - Co-Director of New England Surrogacy
Jennifer White - Co-Director of New England Surrogacy
Bruce Hale - Surrogacy Attorney at Modern Family Law
Alison Zimon, MD - Reproductive Endocrinologist at CCRM Boston
Amber Deming - 2x Gestational Surrogate

Visit NewEnglandSurro.com to learn more!
